{"title":"系统编程","uid":"9ac480373330616bf4900e5e019db089","slug":"OS/系统编程","date":"2020-06-25T04:44:04.000Z","updated":"2022-04-06T09:13:39.000Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/OS/系统编程.json","keywords":null,"cover":"/img/linux.jpeg","content":"<h1 id=\"字\"><a href=\"#字\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"字\"></a>字</h1><p>字节<code>byte</code>，内存单元，8位，如<code>68</code> </p>\n<p>字<code>word</code>，高低字节，16位，如<code>68 A7</code></p>\n<hr>\n<h1 id=\"寄存器\"><a href=\"#寄存器\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"寄存器\"></a>寄存器</h1><p>寄存器16位，两个内存单元(字节)</p>\n<p><code>CS-IP</code>：代码；<code>SS-SP</code>：栈顶；<code>DS-SI/ES-DI</code>：数据</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>寄存器</th>\n<th>主　要　用　途</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody><tr>\n<td>AX</td>\n<td>乘除运算，字的输入输出，中间结果的缓存</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>AL</td>\n<td>字节的乘、除运算，字节的输入输出</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>AH</td>\n<td>字节的乘、除运算，存放中断的功能号</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>BX</td>\n<td>存储器指针</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>BP</td>\n<td>存储器指针、存取堆栈的指针</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>CX</td>\n<td>串操作、循环控制的计数器</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>CL</td>\n<td>移位操作的计数器</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>DX</td>\n<td>字的乘、除运算，间接的输入输出</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>SI</td>\n<td>存储器指针、串指令中的源操作数指针</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>DI</td>\n<td>存储器指针、串指令中的目的操作数指针</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<hr>\n<h1 id=\"栈\"><a href=\"#栈\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"栈\"></a>栈</h1><blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>下-栈底-高地址<br>上-栈顶-低地址<br>push ——sp-2  送入<br>pop  ——读取  sp+2</p></blockquote>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Yveltals/Picgo/%E6%A0%88.png\"></p>\n<hr>\n<h1 id=\"寻址方式\"><a href=\"#寻址方式\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"寻址方式\"></a>寻址方式</h1><p>隐性 mov ax,[bp]   显性 mov ax,ds:[bp]  (避免歧义)<br>用[]表示内存单元，如[bx]，mov ax,[bx]<br>用()表示内存单元或寄存器中的内容，如(ax),(20000H)</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Yveltals/Picgo/%E5%AF%BB%E5%9D%80%E6%96%B9%E5%BC%8F.png\"></p>\n<hr>\n<h1 id=\"数据处理\"><a href=\"#数据处理\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"数据处理\"></a>数据处理</h1><blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p> <code>div</code>    除数8位被除数16位,AX中存放；除数16位被除数32位,DX AX存放高低位</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-textile\" data-language=\"textile\"><code class=\"language-textile\">div  byte  ptr  ds:[0]  &#x2F;&#x2F;8位\n(al)&#x3D;((ax)&#x2F;(ds)*16+0)的商\n(ah)&#x3D;(ax)&#x2F;((ds)*16+0)的余数</code></pre>\n\n<p> <code>mul</code>   8位相乘,乘数默认AL,结果AX；16位相乘,乘数默认AX,DX AX结构高低位</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-textile\" data-language=\"textile\"><code class=\"language-textile\">mul  word ptr [bx+8]  &#x2F;&#x2F;16位\n(ax)&#x3D;(ax)*((ds)*16+(bx)+8)结果的低16位\n(dx)&#x3D;(ax)*((ds)*16+(bx)+8)结果的高16位</code></pre>\n\n<p> <code>db dw dd</code>   定义字节、字、双字型数据</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-textile\" data-language=\"textile\"><code class=\"language-textile\">db  1        &#x2F;&#x2F;01H\ndw  1        &#x2F;&#x2F;0001H\ndd  1        &#x2F;&#x2F;00000001H</code></pre>\n\n<p> <code>dup</code>   定义重复数据</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-textile\" data-language=\"textile\"><code class=\"language-textile\">db  3  dup (1,2) &#x2F;&#x2F;db 1,2,1,2,1,2</code></pre>\n\n<p> <code>movsb  movsw  movsd</code>   数据传送</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-textile\" data-language=\"textile\"><code class=\"language-textile\">源地址是DS:SI,目的地址是ES:DI\nDF&#x3D;0正向传送,DF&#x3D;1反向传送\n在传送完成之后SI和DI会增或减小对应数据长度\n若反复传送，加指令前缀rep并在CX中设置次数 </code></pre></blockquote>\n<hr>\n<h1 id=\"数据长度\"><a href=\"#数据长度\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"数据长度\"></a>数据长度</h1><p>8086CPU中可以指定两种尺寸的数据，byte和word</p>\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><ul>\n<li><p>在有寄存器参与的时候使用寄存器的种类区分</p>\n<ol>\n<li>字：mov ax,1</li>\n<li>字节：mov al,1</li>\n</ol>\n</li>\n<li><p>在没有寄存器参与的时候，使用X ptr指明内存单元长度，X是word或byte </p>\n<ol>\n<li><p>字：mov word ptr ds:[0],1 add word ptr [bx],2    </p>\n</li>\n<li><p>字节：mov byte ptr ds:[0],1 add byte ptr [bx],2</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n</li>\n<li><p>其他默认指明处理类型的指令</p>\n<ol>\n<li>push [1000H]，push默认只进行字操作</li>\n</ol>\n</li>\n</ul></blockquote>\n<p>灵活使用寻址方式的例子，修改下面内存空间中的数据：</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>起始地址</th>\n<th>内容</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody><tr>\n<td>00</td>\n<td>‘DEC’</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>03</td>\n<td>‘Ken Oslen’</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>0C</td>\n<td>137</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>0E</td>\n<td>40</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>10</td>\n<td>‘PDP’</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-assembly\" data-language=\"assembly\"><code class=\"language-assembly\"> ;第三字段改为38\nmov word ptr [bx].0ch,38   \n\n ;修改最后一个字段的三个字符\nmov si,0\nmov byte ptr [bx].10h[si],&#39;v&#39;  \ninc si\nmov byte ptr [bx].10h[si],&#39;A&#39;\ninc si\nmov byte ptr [bx].10h[si],&#39;X&#39;\n\n;类似结构体[i]表示第几个字符</code></pre>\n\n<hr>\n<h1 id=\"编译-amp-Debug\"><a href=\"#编译-amp-Debug\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"编译&amp;Debug\"></a>编译&amp;Debug</h1><h2 id=\"EXE加载过程\"><a href=\"#EXE加载过程\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"EXE加载过程\"></a>EXE加载过程</h2><p>PSP：程序与dos之间通信<br>CX：程序长度<br>DS：程序内存位置<br>CS：程序代码位置(CS&#x3D;DS+10H)</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Yveltals/Picgo/%E5%8A%A0%E8%BD%BD.png\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"Debug\"><a href=\"#Debug\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Debug\"></a>Debug</h2><pre class=\"line-numbers language-textile\" data-language=\"textile\"><code class=\"language-textile\">R：查看，改变CPU寄存器内容\n    直接-r查看寄存器内容\n    -r 寄存器名，改变寄存器内容\nD：查看内存中内容\n    -d直接查看\n    -d 段地址:偏移地址 查看固定地址开始的内容\n    -d 段地址:偏移地址 结尾偏移地址 查看指定范围内存\nE：改写内存中内容\n    -e 起始地址 数据 数据 数据 …\n    提问方式修改 -e 段地址:偏移地址 从这个地址开始一个一个改，空格下一个，回车结束\n    也可以写入字符 ‘a’\nU：将内存中的机器指令翻译成汇编指令\n    -u 段地址:偏移地址\nT：执行一条机器指令\n    -t 执行cs:ip指向的命令\nP：同T单步跟踪，但P命令不会跟踪进入子程序或软中断(跳过循环)\nA：以汇编指令格式在内存中写入一条机器指令\n    -a 段地址:偏移地址 从这个地址开始一行一行的写入汇编语句\nG：g 0012 从当前CS:IP开始一直执行到0012处暂停</code></pre>\n\n<hr>\n<h1 id=\"转移指令\"><a href=\"#转移指令\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"转移指令\"></a>转移指令</h1><p>可以修改IP或同时修改CS，IP的系统指令：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>转移行为：<ol>\n<li>只修改IP，称为段内转移，如jmp ax</li>\n<li>同时修改CS和IP，称为段间转移，如jmp 1000:0</li>\n</ol>\n</li>\n<li>修改范围（段内转移）：<ol>\n<li>短转移：修改IP范围-128~127</li>\n<li>近转移：修改IP范围-32768~32767</li>\n</ol>\n</li>\n<li>转移指令分类：<ol>\n<li>无条件转移：jmp</li>\n<li>条件转移：jcxz</li>\n<li>循环指令：loop</li>\n<li>过程</li>\n<li>中断</li>\n</ol>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"offset指令\"><a href=\"#offset指令\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"offset指令\"></a>offset指令</h2><blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p><code>offset  start</code> : 取得偏移地址</p></blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"jmp指令\"><a href=\"#jmp指令\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"jmp指令\"></a>jmp指令</h2><blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p><code>jmp short 标号</code>：位移字类型8位，段内短转移</p>\n<p><code>jmp near ptr 标号</code>：位移字类型16位，段内近转移</p>\n<p><code>jmp far ptr 标号</code>：段间远转移，机器码中指明目的地址的CS和IP值</p></blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"jcxz指令\"><a href=\"#jcxz指令\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"jcxz指令\"></a>jcxz指令</h2><blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p><code>jcxz 标号</code>：条件转移指令，短转移，如果(cx)&#x3D;0则跳转</p></blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"loop指令\"><a href=\"#loop指令\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"loop指令\"></a>loop指令</h2><blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p><code>loop 标号</code>：循环指令，短转移，如果(cx)!&#x3D;0那么跳转到标号处执行</p></blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"ret-x2F-retf-x2F-iret指令\"><a href=\"#ret-x2F-retf-x2F-iret指令\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"ret&#x2F;retf&#x2F;iret指令\"></a>ret&#x2F;retf&#x2F;iret指令</h2><blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>用栈中的数据修改CS和IP的值，实现近、远转移</p>\n<ul>\n<li><p><code>ret</code> 指令相当于 <code>pop ip</code></p>\n  <pre class=\"line-numbers language-textile\" data-language=\"textile\"><code class=\"language-textile\">(IP)&#x3D;((SS)*16+(SP))\n(SP)&#x3D;(SP)+2</code></pre>\n</li>\n<li><p><code>retf</code> 指令相当于 <code>pop ip, pop cs</code></p>\n  <pre class=\"line-numbers language-textile\" data-language=\"textile\"><code class=\"language-textile\">(IP)&#x3D;((SS)*16+(SP))\n(SP)&#x3D;(SP)+2\n(CS)&#x3D;((SS)*16+(SP))\n(SP)&#x3D;(SP)+2</code></pre>\n</li>\n<li><p><code>iret</code> 指令相当于 <code>pop ip, pop cs, popf</code></p>\n</li>\n</ul></blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"call指令\"><a href=\"#call指令\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"call指令\"></a>call指令</h2><blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>将当前的IP或CS和IP入栈，转移，且位移字类型16位</p>\n<p>call不能实现短转移，但它实现转移的原理和jmp相同。</p>\n<ul>\n<li><code>call 标号</code>相当于 <code>push ip, jmp near ptr 标号</code></li>\n<li><code>call far ptr 标号</code> 相当于 <code>push cs, push ip, jmp far ptr 标号</code></li>\n</ul></blockquote>\n<hr>\n<h1 id=\"标志寄存器\"><a href=\"#标志寄存器\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"标志寄存器\"></a>标志寄存器</h1><p>CPU内部特殊寄存器，用来存储指令执行结果，简称flag寄存器，按位起作用</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Yveltals/Picgo/flag%E5%AF%84%E5%AD%98%E5%99%A8.png\"></p>\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p><code>ZF</code>    零标志位，结果是否为0</p>\n<p><code>PF</code>    奇偶标志位，结果二进制位中1的个数是否偶</p>\n<p><code>SF</code>    符号标志位，结果是否为负；得知有符号数结果正负，对无符号数无意义</p>\n<p><code>CF</code>    进位标志位，记录无符号数运算是否向更高位进&#x2F;借位</p>\n<p><code>OF</code>    溢出标志位，记录有符号数运算是否发生溢出</p>\n<p><code>TF</code>    调试标志位，为1时处理器每次只执行一条指令，即单步执行</p>\n<p><code>IF</code>     中断允许标志位，为1时能响应外部中断，反之则屏蔽</p>\n<p><code>DF</code>    方向标志位，为0则<code>si、di</code>递增，为1递减；<code>cld</code>命令置为0，<code>std</code>置为1</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-none\"><code class=\"language-none\">adc   带进位加法，adc ax, bx 即(ax) &#x3D; (ax)+(bx)+CF\n&#x2F;&#x2F;计算001EF000H + 00201000H，结果放在ax(高16位)和bx(低16位)中\nmov ax, 001EH\nmov bx, 0F000H\nadd bx, 1000H\nadc ax, 0020H   \n&#x2F;&#x2F;高位: ax &#x3D; ax + 0020H +1  (CF保存了进位1)\nsbb   带借位减法，sbb ax,bx 即(ax)&#x3D;(ax)-(bx)-CF</code></pre>\n\n<p><code>cmp</code>    比较指令，<code>cmp ax,bx</code>即<code>(ax)-(bx)</code>，结果正负靠SF(正负)和OF(溢出)共同判断</p></blockquote>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Yveltals/Picgo/flag%E5%AF%84%E5%AD%98%E5%99%A8%E5%90%84%E4%BD%8D%E7%A4%BA%E6%84%8F.png\"></p>\n<hr>\n<h1 id=\"端口\"><a href=\"#端口\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"端口\"></a>端口</h1><h2 id=\"什么是端⼝\"><a href=\"#什么是端⼝\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"什么是端⼝\"></a>什么是端⼝</h2><p>各种存储器都和CPU的地址线、数据线、控制线相连。CPU在操控它们的时候，把它们都当作内存来对待，把它们总的看做⼀个若⼲存储单元组成的逻辑存储器，这个逻辑存储器我们称其为内存地址空间。</p>\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>在PC机系统中，和CPU通过总线相连的芯⽚除各种存储器外，还有以下3种芯⽚。</p>\n<ul>\n<li>各种接⼝卡（⽐如，⽹卡、显卡）上的接⼝芯⽚，它们控制接⼝卡进⾏⼯作；</li>\n<li>主板上的接⼝芯⽚，CPU通过它们对部分外设进⾏访问；</li>\n<li>其他芯⽚，⽤来存储相关的系统信息，或进⾏相关的输⼊输出处理。</li>\n</ul></blockquote>\n<p>在这些芯⽚中，都有⼀组可以由CPU读写的寄存器。这些寄存器都和CPU的总线相连，CPU进⾏读或写的时候都通过控制线向它们所在的芯⽚发出端⼝读写命令。可⻅，从CPU的⻆度，将这些寄存器都当作端⼝，对它们进⾏统⼀编址，从⽽建⽴了⼀个统⼀的端⼝地址空间。</p>\n<p>CPU可以直接读写以下3个地⽅的数据：CPU内部的寄存器、内存单元、端⼝</p>\n<br/>\n\n<h2 id=\"端口的读写\"><a href=\"#端口的读写\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"端口的读写\"></a>端口的读写</h2><blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>在访问端⼝的时候，CPU通过端⼝地址来定位端⼝，因为端⼝所在的芯⽚和CPU通过总线相连，所以，端⼝地址和内存地址⼀样，通过地址总线来传送。在PC系统中，CPU最多可以定位64KB个不同的端⼝。则端⼝地址的范围为0～65535</p>\n<p>端⼝的读写指令只有两条： in 和 out ，分别⽤于从端⼝读取数据和往端⼝写⼊数据</p></blockquote>\n<p>对比CPU执⾏内存访问指令和端⼝访问指令时候，总线上的信息：</p>\n<ol>\n<li><p>访问内存</p>\n <pre class=\"line-numbers language-assembly\" data-language=\"assembly\"><code class=\"language-assembly\">mov ax,ds:[8]                 ;假设执⾏前(ds)&#x3D;0</code></pre>\n\n<ul>\n<li>CPU通过地址线将地址信息8发出</li>\n<li>CPU通过控制线发出内存读写命令，选中存储器芯⽚，并通知它，将要从中读取数据</li>\n<li>存储器将8号单元中的数据通过数据线送⼊CPU</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><p>访问端⼝</p>\n <pre class=\"line-numbers language-assembly\" data-language=\"assembly\"><code class=\"language-assembly\">in al,60h                   ;从60h号端⼝读⼊⼀个字节</code></pre>\n\n<ul>\n<li>CPU通过地址线将地址信息60h发出</li>\n<li>CPU通过控制线发出端⼝读命令，选中端⼝所在的芯⽚，并通知它，将要从中读取数据</li>\n<li>端⼝所在的芯⽚将60h端⼝中的数据通过数据线送⼊CPU</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>注意：</p>\n<p>在 in 和 out 指令中，只能使⽤ ax 或 al 来存放、发送到端⼝中的数据。<br>访问8位端⼝时⽤ al ，访问16位端⼝时⽤ ax 。</p></blockquote>\n<br/>\n\n<h2 id=\"CMOS-RAM芯⽚的读写\"><a href=\"#CMOS-RAM芯⽚的读写\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"CMOS RAM芯⽚的读写\"></a>CMOS RAM芯⽚的读写</h2><p>PC机中，有⼀个CMOS RAM芯⽚，⼀般简称为CMOS。此芯⽚的特征如下:</p>\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>包含⼀个实时时钟和⼀个有128个存储单元的RAM存储器（早期的计算机为64个字节）</p>\n<p>该芯⽚靠电池供电。所以，关机后其内部的实时时钟仍可正常⼯作，RAM中的信息不丢失</p>\n<p>128个字节的RAM中，内部实时时钟占⽤0～0dh单元来保存时间信息，其余⼤部分单元⽤于保存系统配置信息，供系统启动时BIOS程序读取。BIOS也提供了相关的程序，使我们可以在开机的时候配置CMOS RAM中的系统信息</p>\n<p>该芯⽚内部有两个端⼝，端⼝地址为<code>70h</code>和<code>71h</code>。CPU通过这两个端⼝来读写CMOS RAM</p>\n<p><code>70h</code>为地址端⼝，存放要访问的CMOS RAM单元的地址；<code>71h</code>为数据端⼝，存放从选定的CMOS RAM单元中读取的数据，或要写⼊到其中的数据。可⻅，CPU对CMOS RAM的读写分两步进⾏。⽐如，读CMOS RAM的2号单元：将2送⼊端⼝<code>70h</code>；从端⼝<code>71h</code>读出2号单元的内容</p></blockquote>\n<hr>\n<h1 id=\"程序编写\"><a href=\"#程序编写\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"程序编写\"></a>程序编写</h1><h2 id=\"显存显示字符串\"><a href=\"#显存显示字符串\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"显存显示字符串\"></a>显存显示字符串</h2><details class=\"custom-details\">\n<summary>Click to see more</summary>\n<p><pre class=\"line-numbers language-assembly\" data-language=\"assembly\"><code class=\"language-assembly\">assume cs:code\n\ndata segment\n    db &#39;welcome to masm!&#39; \ndata ends\n\ncode segment\nstart:\n    mov ax,data\n    mov ds,ax\n\n    &#x2F;&#x2F;显存地址 ES:DI\n    mov ax,0b800h\n    mov es,ax\n    mov di,10*160+80 ; \n\n    &#x2F;&#x2F;数据地址 DS:SI\n    mov si,0\n    mov cx,16\ns1:\n    mov al,ds:[si]  &#x2F;&#x2F;低位字符\n    mov ah,00000010B ; &#x2F;&#x2F;高位颜色\n    mov es:[di],ax\n    inc si\n    add di,2\n    loop s1\n\n    mov ax, 4c00h\n    int 21h ;\ncode ends\nend start</code></pre>\n\n</p>\n</details>\n<h2 id=\"除法溢出中断程序\"><a href=\"#除法溢出中断程序\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"除法溢出中断程序\"></a>除法溢出中断程序</h2><details class=\"custom-details\">\n<summary>Click to see more</summary>\n<p><pre class=\"line-numbers language-assembly\" data-language=\"assembly\"><code class=\"language-assembly\">assume cs:code\ncode segment\n\nstart:\nmov ax,cs\nmov ds,ax\nmov si,offset do\nmov ax,0\nmov es,ax\nmov di,200h\n\nmov cx,offset doend-offset do ; 安装中断例程\ncld\nrep movsb\n\nmov word ptr es:[0],200h\nmov word ptr es:[2],0 ; 设置中断向量表\n\nmov dx,0ffffh\nmov bx,1 ; 测试一下\ndiv bx\n\nmov ax, 4c00h\nint 21h \n\ndo:jmp short dostart\ndb &#39;divide error!&#39;\ndostart:\nmov ax,0\nmov ds,ax\nmov si,202h\n\nmov ax,0b800h\nmov es,ax\nmov di,160*12+60\n\nmov cx,13\ns:\nmov al,ds:[si]\nmov ah,2\nmov es:[di],ax\ninc si\nadd di,2\nloop s\n\nmov ax, 4c00h\nint 21h\n\ndoend:nop\n\ncode ends\nend start</code></pre>\n\n</p>\n</details>\n<h2 id=\"利用中断和栈实现loop\"><a href=\"#利用中断和栈实现loop\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"利用中断和栈实现loop\"></a>利用中断和栈实现loop</h2><p>原题：在屏幕中间显示80个<code>！</code></p>\n<p>参数：<code>(cx)</code>&#x3D;循环次数，<code>(bx)</code>&#x3D;位移</p>\n<details class=\"custom-details\">\n<summary>Click to see more</summary>\n<p><pre class=\"line-numbers language-assembly\" data-language=\"assembly\"><code class=\"language-assembly\">assume cs:code\ncode segment\nstart:\n    mov ax,cs\n    mov ds,ax\n    mov si,offset lp\n    mov ax,0\n    mov es,ax\n    mov di,200h\n\n    mov cx,offset lpend-offset lp ; 安装中断例程\n    cld\n    rep movsb\n\n    mov word ptr es:[7ch*4],200h\n    mov word ptr es:[7ch*4+2],0 ; 设置中断向量表\n\n    mov ax,0b800h\n    mov es,ax\n    mov di,160*12\n    mov bx,offset s-offset se ;设置回退位移\n    mov cx,80            ;设置loop次数\ns:mov byte ptr es:[di],&#39;!&#39; ; 完成第一次显示\n    add di,2\n    int 7ch ;测试int 7ch\nse:nop\n\n    mov ax, 4c00h\n    int 21h\n\nlp: ;中断例程\n    dec cx\n    jcxz f\n    push bp   ;修改bp前先保存\n    mov bp,sp  ;SP指向栈顶，即存入的IP\n    add [bp+2],bx  ;指针回退位移....为什么+2？？？？\nf: pop bp\n    iret\n    lpend:nop\n\ncode ends\nend start</code></pre>\n</p>\n</details>\n<hr>\n<h1 id=\"注意\"><a href=\"#注意\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"注意\"></a>注意</h1><blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>1.对<code>mov ax,[0]</code>，Debug指内存数据，masm指0，可用段前缀区分如<code>mov al，ds:[0]</code></p>\n<p>2.数据不能以字母开头，大于<code>9fffH</code>的数据在开头加0，如<code>0A000H</code></p>\n<p>3.子程序要先将<code>所用到的寄存器</code>存到栈里</p>\n<p>4.使用<code>&#39;xxx&#39;</code>的方式指明数据是以字符形式给出的，编译器会自动将它们转化为ASCII码</p></blockquote>\n","feature":true,"text":"字字节byte，内存单元，8位，如68 字word，高低字节，16位，如68 A7 寄存器寄存器16位，两个内存单元(字节) CS-IP：代码；SS-SP：栈顶；DS-SI/ES-DI：数据 寄存器 主 要 用 途 AX 乘除运算，字的输入输出，中间结果的缓存 AL 字节的乘、除...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"7.1k","symbolsTime":"6 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"OS","slug":"OS","count":5,"path":"api/categories/OS.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"系统编程","slug":"系统编程","count":2,"path":"api/tags/系统编程.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%AD%97\"><span class=\"toc-text\">字</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%AF%84%E5%AD%98%E5%99%A8\"><span class=\"toc-text\">寄存器</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E6%A0%88\"><span class=\"toc-text\">栈</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%AF%BB%E5%9D%80%E6%96%B9%E5%BC%8F\"><span class=\"toc-text\">寻址方式</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%E5%A4%84%E7%90%86\"><span class=\"toc-text\">数据处理</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%E9%95%BF%E5%BA%A6\"><span class=\"toc-text\">数据长度</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E7%BC%96%E8%AF%91-amp-Debug\"><span class=\"toc-text\">编译&amp;Debug</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class