":"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20210313122054101.png","link":"/","description":"","socials":{"github":"","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{}}}},"next_post":{"title":"中断","uid":"87122f1313843578dbea5a21e7a0d4c1","slug":"OS/中断","date":"2020-06-25T04:22:04.000Z","updated":"2022-04-06T09:13:39.000Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/OS/中断.json","keywords":null,"cover":"/img/os.jpeg","text":"内中断内中断的产生 除法错误:0 单步执行:1 执行 into 指令:4 执行 int 指令,格式为int n ,n为字节型立即数,是中断类型码 中断过程 由中断类型码找到中断向量,并自动用它设置 CS和IP，随后执行中断处理程序 从中断信息取得中断类型码N pushf &#x2...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"1.2k","symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"OS","slug":"OS","count":5,"path":"api/categories/OS.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"中断","slug":"中断","count":1,"path":"api/tags/中断.json"}],"author":{"name":"Yveltal","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20210313122054101.png","link":"/","description":"","socials":{"github":"","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{}}}}}